{"lemma":"زَفِر","slug":"زَفِر","root":"ز.ف.ر","root_slug":"ز-ف-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ز-ف-ر","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n17864","","n17866","n17867","n17868"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B2%D9%8E%D9%81%D9%90%D8%B1"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to exhale","tags":["intransitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to bray","tags":["intransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"زَفَرَ ٱلْحِمَارُ","english":"The donkey brayed."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/za.fa.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n17864","headword_ar":"زَفَرَ","root":"zfr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafiyrN","text_ar":"زَفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raforN","text_ar":"رَفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_izofiyrN","text_ar":"اـِزْفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iroziyzN","text_ar":"اـِرْزِيزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", app. an inf. n., or perhaps a simple subst.,])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew in his breath to the utmost, by reason of distress:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) it originally signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he drew back his breath vehemently, so that his ribs became swollen out:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib:)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafiyrN","text_ar":"زَفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beginning of the cry of the ass,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, A, Er-Rághib,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and of the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth,) and is generally used in this sense; (Er-Rághib;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ahiyqN","text_ar":"شَهِيقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the ending thereof; (Lth, S, A, Er-Rághib;) for the former is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drawing in of the breath,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the latter is the sending it forth: (Lth, S:) or the verb signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sent forth his breath, after prolonging it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sent forth his breath with a prolonged sound:"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sighed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"uttered a long sigh,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sighed vehemently;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he groaned:"},{"kind":"text","text":"] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he filled his chest, by reason of grief, and then sent forth his breath:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he breathed, raising his voice, like one moaning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in grief."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 20.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafarati Aln~aAru","text_ar":"زَفَرَتِ النَّارُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The fire made a sound to be heard from its burning,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its fierce burning:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) and this [sounding] is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafiyrN","text_ar":"زَفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HadomN","text_ar":"حَدْمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; where"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaforN","text_ar":"زَفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", its inf. n., is expl., on the authority of AZ, as signifying The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flaming,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"blazing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of fire.] And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlbaHoru yazofiru bitamaw~ujihi","text_ar":"البَحْرُ يَزْفِرُ بِتَمَوُّجِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sea makes a roaring by its tumultuousness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafarati AlA^aroDu","text_ar":"زَفَرَتِ الاَرْضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The land put forth its plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafara","text_ar":"زَفَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaforN","text_ar":"زَفْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Azdfr","text_ar":"ازدفر","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He carried,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K,) a thing, (K,) or a load, or burden, (S, A,) as, for ex., a filled water-skin. (TA.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazofiruwna Eanohu AlA^avoqaAla","text_ar":"يَزْفِرُونَ عَنْهُ الاَثْقَالَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They bear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"carry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"take off from him, and carry, his burdens"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He drew,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and carried,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) water. (K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","A","Lth","M","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n17866","headword_ar":"زِفْرٌ","root":"zfr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A load,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burden,"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimolN","text_ar":"حِمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) on the back, (K,) or on the head,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that is heavy, and in consequence of which the bearer breathes vehemently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"groans"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazofiru","text_ar":"يَزْفِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (A:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^azofaArN","text_ar":"اَزْفَارٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, A.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water-skin of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qirobap","text_ar":"قِرْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a skin in which a pastor carries his water:"},{"kind":"text","text":"pl. as above. (TA.) ―         -b3-  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparatus of a traveller,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comprising the water-skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (TA.)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1237},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lamb;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamalN","text_ar":"حَمَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": so in the Bári'. (K.) This signification and that of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HimolN","text_ar":"حِمْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"are both correct. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","A","K"]},{"entry_id":"n17867","headword_ar":"زَفَرٌ","root":"zfr","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A prop"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a tree. (K, TA.)       -A2-  [In modern Arabic, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Grease, greasy food,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"flesh-meat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"app. from the Pers."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafaro","text_ar":"زَفَرْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafor","text_ar":"زَفْر"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying “ filth: ” and hence,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscenity."},{"kind":"text","text":"Hence also the vulgar epithet"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zifir","text_ar":"زِفِر"},{"kind":"text","text":"(app. for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafirN","text_ar":"زَفِرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"), meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Greasy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filthy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obscene."},{"kind":"text","text":"See 5.]"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n17868","headword_ar":"زُفَرٌ","root":"zfr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sea,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that makes a roaring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazofiru","text_ar":"يَزْفِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of its tumultuousness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A river containing much water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so that it resembles a sea."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A large gift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) as likened to a sea. (TA.) ―         -b4-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A liberal man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"likened to a sea that makes a roaring, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yazofiru","text_ar":"يَزْفِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) by reason of its tumultuousness; (A;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAfirapN","text_ar":"زَافِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who carries loads,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"burdens;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"who has strength to carry water-skins."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAfirapN","text_ar":"زَافِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b6-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"One who has power to bear responsibilities."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, S. *) ―         -b7-  Hence, (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lord, master, chief,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or, for the same reason,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great lord,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAfirapN","text_ar":"زَافِرَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K, TA.) ―         -b8-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A courageous man."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, * TA.) ―         -b9-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b10-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaAfirapN","text_ar":"زَافِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places: ―         -b11-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zafiyrN","text_ar":"زَفِيرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["K","S"]}]}}